ygData.messageBody:
Ok here is my story

Last night I saw a someone auction off a Staff of Withering. It is a staff
that I am very interested in. I offer the person 400pp and a Goss robe. He
aggread, but said I would have to go the keldean to get the staff from one of
his other char. I said fine for that staff I would do just about anything. So
here I go trecking from Permafrost all the way to Neriak. Die once from the
damn Highhold cht's. Well I get to the bank in Neriak. Pow I find out iv only
got 358pp in the bank. Sence I cant meet the whole 400pp I offer him a water
crystal staff on top of the 358pp and the goss robe. Water Crystal staff are
curently going tor 100pp. He ingornes me. Doent even reply. I say ok. and
offher a dragon dirk on top of all the rest. He says he is sorry but he has
been offered 500pp and going to take it.

I go off. After all this time he has wated me trecking all the way accross
the content. He would be so fucking greedy. excuse my language. Granted I did
fall short 42pp of our deal. But I made up for it and then some, but no he
wanted to twink one of his friends withe a blackend iron bastard sword.

Wel here is my worning Watch our for a lev34 gnome Necro by the name is
Nihilist on the bristlebane server.

The favor Please do not do business with this *&*&*^&^&%^%$.

thanks for listening
Wampir
